Class Player

Player
public class Player extends Object
The Player class represents a player in a team.

      public Player(String firstName, String lastName, LocalDate birthDate, Position preferredPosition, Position assignedPosition, int skillLevel) throws IllegalArgumentException

      Parameters:
      firstName - String object stands for the first name of the player
      lastName - String object stands for the last name of the player
      birthDate - LocalDate object stands for the birthdate of the player
      preferredPosition - Enum object stands for the preferred position of the player
      assignedPosition - Enum object stands for the actual position of the player
      skillLevel - int object in [1, 5] stands for the skill level of the player
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException
